{"tid":447822,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"致 最愛的前度","createTime":"2017-10-25T16:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T07:44:28.000Z","uid":9792,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"12e7f0abfbcbbace5791bed8f4b686ad59237adc","tid":447822,"uid":9792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:00:12.000Z","msg":"今天是前度的生日<br />\n你將我所有可以搵到你嘅途徑都封鎖了<br />\n我只好係到同你講聲生日快樂 我仲好掛住你<br />\n我知我係你心目中已經再冇任何位置<br />\n但我仲係好愛你好掛住你<br />\n見到個女人好似同你好幸福<br />\n我都只好祝福你 雖然我仍妄想你會返黎<br />\n上次同你講我鍾意咗第個<br />\n其實我根本冇 係我口硬唔想你睇死我<br />\n但原來我根本呃唔到自己我仲好掛住你<br />\n我試過迫自己鍾意其他人<br />\n最後都係做唔到<br />\n可能你都已經唔會再諗起我<br />\n但我每日都仲會不停諗你<br />\n如果可以我真係好想你可以返黎我身邊..<br />\n親愛的 我愛你 我希望你永遠快樂..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f8bf7e4cf5121231f6ce8201f307fe1c269514","tid":447822,"uid":99346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:01:12.000Z","msg":"放過自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7905eb1f392b955d19387bc7a36c41b95683d46b","tid":447822,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:02:11.000Z","msg":"Ok 返黎同你扑一晚野"},{"pid":"b6a14019c5df13a3f51bd66900d6fc461c6724a3","tid":447822,"uid":9792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放過自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想 做唔到<br />\n好愛佢.."},{"pid":"32dc22e8a6ce36c5ef08905e6b3544088d51bf56","tid":447822,"uid":9792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:06:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ok 返黎同你扑一晚野</blockquote><br />\n好阿返黎就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32760f5633dc2b481f62f124c7a2f473d8c3b235","tid":447822,"uid":3613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232410612c66